---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import SEO from '@/components/SEO.astro'
---

<BaseLayout>
  <SEO 
    title="Shipping Policy | AI DevOps" 
    description="Shipping and delivery policy for AI DevOps training services and digital products."
    slot="seo"
  />
  
  <article class="prose prose-invert max-w-4xl mx-auto py-16 px-4">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Shipping Policy</h1>
    
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <p class="text-gray-300">
        This shipping policy outlines the delivery terms for our training services and digital products offered through our Platform.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Digital Training Services</h2>
      
      <div class="bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-emerald-300 font-semibold mb-2">Live Training Sessions</h3>
        <p class="text-emerald-200">
          All our DevOps training sessions are conducted online via video conferencing platforms. There is no physical shipping involved.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-200">Delivery Timeline:</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-300">
          <li><strong>Session Scheduling:</strong> Within 24 hours of payment confirmation</li>
          <li><strong>Calendar Invite:</strong> Sent immediately after scheduling</li>
          <li><strong>Preparation Materials:</strong> Shared 48 hours before the session</li>
          <li><strong>Session Recording:</strong> Available within 24 hours after completion</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Digital Materials Delivery</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <p class="text-gray-300">
          For training sessions, we provide the following digital materials:
        </p>
        
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-300">
          <li><strong>Session Preparation Guide:</strong> Delivered via email 48 hours before training</li>
          <li><strong>Training Materials:</strong> Shared during the live session via screen sharing</li>
          <li><strong>Session Recording:</strong> Provided via secure link within 24 hours</li>
          <li><strong>Certificate of Completion:</strong> Issued within 48 hours after session completion</li>
          <li><strong>Follow-up Resources:</strong> Additional learning materials sent within 72 hours</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Delivery Methods</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-zinc-800/50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-zinc-700">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Email Delivery</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm">
            All digital materials are delivered to the email address provided during booking. Please ensure your email is correct and check spam folders.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-zinc-800/50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-zinc-700">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Secure Links</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm">
            Session recordings and large files are shared via secure, time-limited links to protect your privacy and data security.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Technical Requirements</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <p class="text-gray-300">
          To receive our training services, you need:
        </p>
        
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-300">
          <li>Stable internet connection (minimum 2 Mbps)</li>
          <li>Computer/laptop with webcam and microphone</li>
          <li>Updated web browser (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, or Edge)</li>
          <li>Email access for receiving materials and links</li>
          <li>Valid email address for all communications</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Delivery Issues & Support</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <p class="text-gray-300">
          If you don't receive any materials within the specified timeframe:
        </p>
        
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-300">
          <li>Check your spam/junk email folder</li>
          <li>Verify your email address is correct</li>
          <li>Contact us immediately at <a href="mailto:ritikvirus6@gmail.com" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300">ritikvirus6@gmail.com</a></li>
          <li>Provide your transaction ID for faster resolution</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-yellow-500/10 border border-yellow-500/20 rounded-lg p-4">
        <h3 class="text-yellow-300 font-semibold mb-2">Important Note</h3>
        <p class="text-yellow-200 text-sm">
          Since all our services are digital and delivered online, there are no physical shipping charges or delivery fees. All delivery timelines mentioned above are in IST (Indian Standard Time).
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Contact for Delivery Issues</h2>
      
      <div class="bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-600/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-blue-200 mb-2"><strong>Email:</strong> ritikvirus6@gmail.com</p>
        <p class="text-blue-200 mb-2"><strong>Phone:</strong> +91 8920279167</p>
        <p class="text-blue-200 mb-2"><strong>Response Time:</strong> Within 24 hours</p>
        <p class="text-blue-200"><strong>Office Hours:</strong> Monday - Friday (9:00 - 18:00 IST)</p>
      </div>

      <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mt-8">
        This shipping policy is effective as of the date of your purchase and may be updated from time to time. Please check this page periodically for any changes.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>